#: fca-multi-reactions.php
msgid ""
"FCA Multi-Reactions requires Fluent Community to be installed and activated."
msgstr "FCA Multi-Reactions 需要安裝並啟動 Fluent Community。"

#: includes/class-reactions-api.php
msgid "You must be logged in to react."
msgstr "您必須登入才能發表評論。"

#: includes/class-reactions-api.php
msgid "Invalid object ID."
msgstr "無效的物件 ID。"

#: includes/class-reactions-api.php
msgid "Invalid reaction type."
msgstr "無效的反應類型。"

#: includes/class-reactions-api.php
msgid "Reaction added successfully."
msgstr "反應已成功新增。"

#: includes/class-reactions-api.php
msgid "You must be logged in to remove reaction."
msgstr "您必須登入才能刪除評論。"

#: includes/class-reactions-api.php
msgid "Reaction removed successfully."
msgstr "反應物已成功去除。"

#: includes/class-reactions-api.php
msgid "No valid feed IDs provided."
msgstr "未提供有效的訂閱源 ID。"

#: includes/class-reactions-api.php
msgid "You must be logged in to update reactions."
msgstr "您必須登入才能更新評論。"

#: includes/class-reactions-api.php
msgid "No existing reaction found to update."
msgstr "找不到可更新的現有反應。"

#: includes/class-reactions-api.php
msgid "Reaction type updated successfully."
msgstr "反應類型已成功更新。"

#: includes/class-reactions-api.php
msgid "Failed to update reaction type."
msgstr "反應類型更新失敗。"

#: includes/class-reactions-admin.php views/admin-settings.php
msgid "FCA Multi-Reactions Settings"
msgstr "FCA多重反應設定"

#: includes/class-reactions-admin.php
msgid "Multi-Reactions"
msgstr "多反應"

#: includes/class-reactions-admin.php
msgid "Settings have been reset to defaults."
msgstr "設定已重設為預設值。"

#: includes/class-reactions-admin.php
msgid "Settings saved."
msgstr "設定已儲存。"

#: views/admin-settings.php
msgid "Save Settings"
msgstr "儲存設定"

#: views/admin-settings.php
msgid "General Settings"
msgstr "常規設定"

#: views/admin-settings.php
msgid "Enable Multi-Reactions"
msgstr "啟用多重反應"

#: views/admin-settings.php
msgid "Replace default heart reactions with multi-reactions"
msgstr "將預設心臟反應替換為多重反應"

#: views/admin-settings.php
msgid ""
"When enabled, the default Fluent Community heart reaction will be replaced "
"with multiple reaction options."
msgstr "啟用後，Fluent Community 的預設心形表情將會被多個表情選項取代。"

#: views/admin-settings.php
msgid "Enable Comment Reactions"
msgstr "啟用評論反應"

#: views/admin-settings.php
msgid "Enable reaction functionality on comments"
msgstr "啟用留言回應功能"

#: views/admin-settings.php
msgid ""
"When enabled, users can react to comments with multiple emoji options. If "
"disabled, comments will use the default Fluent Community reaction system."
msgstr ""
"啟用此功能後，使用者可以使用多種表情符號選項回應評論。如果停用此功能，則評論"
"將使用 Fluent Community 的預設回覆系統。"

#: views/admin-settings.php
msgid "Comment Reaction Emoji"
msgstr "評論表情符號"

#: views/admin-settings.php
msgid ""
"Choose which emoji to use for comment reactions (replaces the default heart)."
msgstr "選擇用於評論反應的表情符號（替換預設的愛心）。"

#: views/admin-settings.php
msgid "Counter Display Emojis"
msgstr "櫃檯展示表情符號"

#: views/admin-settings.php
msgid ""
"How many reaction emojis to show in the counter summary next to reaction "
"counts."
msgstr "在反應計數旁邊的計數器摘要中顯示多少個反應表情符號？"

#: views/admin-settings.php
msgid "Emoji Overlap"
msgstr "表情符號重疊"

#: views/admin-settings.php
msgid ""
"How much the emojis overlap each other in the summary. Higher = more overlap."
msgstr "摘要中表情符號的重疊程度。數值越高，重疊越多。"

#: views/admin-settings.php
msgid "Emoji Stroke"
msgstr "表情符號描邊"

#: views/admin-settings.php
msgid "Border thickness around each emoji to create visual separation."
msgstr "每個表情符號周圍都有加粗的邊框，以創造視覺上的分隔感。"

#: views/admin-settings.php
msgid "Reaction Types"
msgstr "反應類型"

#: views/admin-settings.php
msgid ""
"Configure the available reaction types. Drag to reorder, toggle to enable/"
"disable."
msgstr "設定可用的反應類型。拖曳即可重新排序，切換即可啟用/停用。"

#: views/admin-settings.php
msgid "+ Add"
msgstr "+ 新增"

#: views/admin-settings.php
msgid "Note:"
msgstr "筆記："

#: views/admin-settings.php
msgid ""
"Changing or disabling reactions will not affect existing reactions in the "
"database. They will simply not be displayed."
msgstr "更改或停用反應不會影響資料庫中已有的反應。它們只會不再顯示。"

#: views/admin-settings.php
msgid "Reset to Defaults"
msgstr "恢復預設設定"
